---

This project depends on but does NOT redistribute the upstream proxy itself.
The upstream "deepseek-cursor-proxy" is a separate MIT-licensed work by
Yixing Lao, fetched at install time from:

    https://github.com/yxlao/deepseek-cursor-proxy

All credit for the proxy core (the `reasoning_content` recovery logic, the
SQLite cache, the ngrok integration, the streaming SSE rewriter, etc.) goes
to that project. This repository only adds a Windows system-tray supervisor
that wraps the proxy with lifecycle management, a watchdog, a state machine,
and GUI configuration windows.
